# VektrIDE Dashboard Build

## Setup
- [ ] Initialize Vite + React project in `c:\VektrIDE`
- [ ] Install dependencies (Monaco Editor, Playwright, Express, etc.)

## Backend
- [ ] Create `ide-backend.js` — Playwright bridge to Gemini
- [ ] Create `server.js` — Express API server (file browsing, Gemini relay, file save)

## Frontend
- [ ] Build sidebar file explorer component
- [ ] Build Monaco Editor integration
- [ ] Build "Ask Gemini" prompt UI + button
- [ ] Build split-view terminal panel for Gemini response
- [ ] Build "Confirm Change" button to save code to file
- [ ] Style the full dashboard (dark theme, premium design)

## Verification
- [ ] Start dev server and verify UI renders
- [ ] Test file browsing endpoint
- [ ] Test Gemini ask flow end-to-end via browser
